{"tid":2492684,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港鐵惡晒｜遭壓頸青年雙手麻痺仍留院 目擊者批港鐵職員：點解要郁手郁腳？","createTime":"2021-04-17T10:08:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-17T11:47:27.000Z","uid":44209,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"4df0f594c26eb093ef7eaf40be775c1531df2e6e","tid":2492684,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T10:08:39.000Z","msg":"港鐵殘疾歧視<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n自反修例運動起，港鐵嚴打持特惠票乘車人士，昨日（16日）一名為精神病殘疾的青年持特惠票出閘，5名職員立即截查，疑惹起對方不滿，結果演變成「5對1」、有如執法人員制服市民的戲碼，最後警方大陣仗持盾到場，將青年拘捕。有目擊事發經過的市民批評港鐵行政失當，事件對被捕青年不公平。<br />\n<br />\n昨晨一名持有殘疾證明的青年，於港鐵杏花邨站出閘時，疑因使用特惠車票，被港鐵職員截停查票，他情緒激動，及後被數名職員制服地上，糾纏期間職員一度疑用手踭壓頸的動作。當時，正在上班途中的註冊社工，兼詠春散打教練柯清泉經過現場，為保障青年安全，即參與調停。<br />\n<br />\n柯今日現身評論事件，表示雖明白職員截查本意，但認為事件涉及港鐵決策失當。「係（青年）打人先？定係（職員）引起糾紛先？」他首先評論港鐵職員制服行為，或使用不必要武力。柯自18歲起擔任詠春散打教練多年，師承葉正，熟知各部分被攻擊的危險。其中，他認為職員手踭壓頸的動作危險。他解釋，壓頸動作有可能影響血液經動脈上腦，長時間受壓可能會導致昏厥，甚至令腦部缺氧或成植物人，認為職員應制服青年手腳，不應隨便使出「叉頸」或「撳頭」等動作。<br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210417/7DZ2VCZATZGA5HPHBGE4TEWOIU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210417%2F7DZ2VCZATZGA5HPHBGE4TEWOIU%2F&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CL6Zg5fsFimH5gYFReGFrXmU%3D&h=6a03774b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210417%2F7DZ2VCZATZGA5HPHBGE4TEWOIU%2F&h=800c9083\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210417/7DZ2VCZATZGA5HPHBGE4TEWOIU/</a>"},{"pid":"a412188873ff96e1f0b2524f72bcb2199052de81","tid":2492684,"uid":47356,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T10:09:59.000Z","msg":"去信比澳洲鐵路講虐待傷殘人仕"},{"pid":"1226109f69c63ab7dd317ec9b4091dc846203f82","tid":2492684,"uid":51271,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"a412188873ff96e1f0b2524f72bcb2199052de81","tid":2492684,"uid":47356,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T10:09:59.000Z","msg":"去信比澳洲鐵路講虐待傷殘人仕"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T10:11:00.000Z","msg":"仲有瑞典、倫敦"},{"pid":"284c8a0a729d791c9491596d25e98323ffb99281","tid":2492684,"uid":44209,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1226109f69c63ab7dd317ec9b4091dc846203f82","tid":2492684,"uid":51271,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"a412188873ff96e1f0b2524f72bcb2199052de81","tid":2492684,"uid":47356,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T10:09:59.000Z","msg":"去信比澳洲鐵路講虐待傷殘人仕"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T10:11:00.000Z","msg":"仲有瑞典、倫敦"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T10:11:50.000Z","msg":"美國左膠應該都會care呢啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b80c568d907f99c3e4ae5af7dbbe19ebc2879799","tid":2492684,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"284c8a0a729d791c9491596d25e98323ffb99281","tid":2492684,"uid":44209,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1226109f69c63ab7dd317ec9b4091dc846203f82","tid":2492684,"uid":51271,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"a412188873ff96e1f0b2524f72bcb2199052de81","tid":2492684,"uid":47356,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T10:09:59.000Z","msg":"去信比澳洲鐵路講虐待傷殘人仕"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T10:11:00.000Z","msg":"仲有瑞典、倫敦"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T10:11:50.000Z","msg":"美國左膠應該都會care呢啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T10:12:51.000Z","msg":"美國無黨鐵服務"},{"pid":"b7f347c88d156b4c5b9b9f6cffda10a920cd7f88","tid":2492684,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T10:13:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adf8dc833935e85168324fa356af62902a7217a4","tid":2492684,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score